            <note xml:id="foot.f1">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-12930.xml">letter from W. R. Browne, 21 December 1880</ref>. Browne had invited CD to a conference at Lambeth Palace, London, about the compatibility of modern science with religious belief.</note>
